title: Tongits
description: Tongits is a three-player card game that is still in the Rummy family. The objective of the game is to empty your hand cards by forming sets(melds) or minimize the total score when a fight is called or when the central stack is empty. Each player will be dealt 12 cards while the dealer gets 13, and the rest of the cards are left as a draw card. The game begins when the dealer dumps a card. The next person can either pick up the disposed card if that card makes a set or adds to a set they already have or get one from the central stack. Collect hand combinations and dump unnecessary cards. The picking and discarding of cards goes on until someone wins by Tongits, calls a fight, or until the central stack runs out of cards. If this happens, the players tally the points of the cards they have in hand, and the one with the lowest wins. To call a fight, the player needs to put down a meld on the table, and no player drops any card on any of their melds in that round. If the player can use all of their cards in combinations by connecting to opponents’ or the exposed card sets, or if the player gets rid of all their cards, then the player wins by Tongits. Have fun with your friends, enjoy exciting moments, and relieve your stress every day!

description: Tangled Ropes is a captivating knot-solving adventure that tests your mental agility and dexterity. Challenge yourself with intricate, mind-bending puzzles as you work through complex knots that grow more challenging with each level. Sharpen your problem-solving skills and unravel each knot to progress in this unique puzzle journey!

title: Dice Roll: Protect the Relic
description: Dice Roll: Protect the Relic is a tower defense game that combines strategic dice-rolling with magical combat. You’ll defend an ancient relic from enemy waves by rolling dice with unique powers like fireballs, ice barriers, and healing spells. Each roll activates different abilities, making every move crucial to your survival.

title: The Bottle Boy
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(Android), Steam
description: The Bottle Boy is a 3D puzzle platformer game where friendship is at the heart of every challenge! You play as a groovy, breakdancing Glass Bottle with a mission: to save Corky the Dog from a looming tsunami. To rescue your best friend, you'll need to fill up with water, solve math and logic puzzles, and dance your way through obstacles across a vibrant, hip-hop-inspired world. Along the way, collect photos to exchange at the HIP STYLE HOP STORE and unlock cool new looks. Get ready for a journey filled with love, puzzles, and endless style!

title: Build And Run
description: Run, build, and conquer! Construct missing parts of the level while running, using ramps, slopes, and horizontal builds. Arm yourself with knives, guns, and TNT to defeat enemies and clear obstacles. Enjoy Level Mode or Endless Mode, and spend earned coins in the shop to customize your character with stylish hats and shoes.

title: Island Builder
description: Island Builder is a building game that offers both relaxing and fun gameplay that challenges you to strategically place various buildings to get maximum points. Use your logic to achieve objectives to progress through levels successfully. This game is ideal for you to enjoy in your free time. Explore new islands, and aim for a high score!

title: Fisquarium
description: Fisquarium is an idle clicker game that combines the joy of clicking with the soothing atmosphere of an aquarium. In this game, players click to earn fish, unlock diverse species, enhance production through upgrades, discover new fish types, collect trophies, and immerse themselves in the relaxing world of aquatic wonders. Whether you're a casual player or an avid clicker fan, Fisquarium offers a laid-back and enjoyable experience!

title: Cookie Hangman
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)
description: Cookie Hangman is an engaging puzzle game that invites you to become a Hangman champion with a sweet twist. Embark on a delightful word-guessing adventure, where you must unravel hidden words to save an adorable cookie character from the clutches of becoming a hangman. The game offers over 500 levels of mind-teasing puzzles to keep you hooked. Dress up your cookie character with a variety of outfits, each offering additional lives or moves to enhance your gameplay. Utilize power-ups like bombs and hints when you're stuck, and open treasure chests to reveal rewards like coins, bombs, and hints. The game not only entertains but also enhances your vocabulary and word-guessing skills. With vibrant visuals, captivating animations, and customization options, Cookie Hangman is a delightful and educational choice for players of all ages. Start your word-guessing adventure now and save the cookie character from becoming a hangman!

title: Isometric Escape 2
description: Isometric Escape 2 is a challenging escape game where you need to solve a series of puzzles in order to escape from isometric rooms. Use your logic and memory to find useful objects and solve riddles. With an isometric perspective, the game offers a unique visual experience as players navigate through the rooms.

title: Air Battle Royale: Sky Blitz
description: Air Battle Royale: Sky Blitz is an airplane shooting game where you take command of a heavily armed fighter jet. With just a single finger, you'll effortlessly soar through the skies, hunting down rivals and locking onto targets for intense dogfights. Win battles, earn rewards, and amp up your aircraft's speed and firepower or unlock even mightier planes. So, gear up, pilot – ascend to the skies and reign supreme as the ultimate ace in this high-flying extravaganza!

title: Save The Worm: Draw Puzzle
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)
description: Save The Worm: Draw Puzzle is a puzzle drawing game to help you train your brain effectively. Use your freehand drawing skills to help the worm go inside its cocoon so it can evolve.

title: Stickman Fighting: Super War
description: Stickman Fighting: Super War is a ragdoll physics game where you fight with other stickman warriors and be the supreme hero. Choose your weapon and attack enemies in this epic stickman battleground!

title: Paint By Words
description: Paint By Words is a unique blend of word and picture puzzles, offering a relaxing yet challenging meta-puzzle experience. Solve creative word puzzles to unlock beautiful artwork and complete stunning artistic challenges.

title: Smash N Collect
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)
description: Smash N Collect is a lively arcade game where your mission is to destroy and collect colorful items. Tap on two or more connected identical objects to smash them and trigger powerful combos. Enjoy the dynamic physics that adds excitement to every move. As you progress, explore beautiful locations, solve countless puzzles, and participate in thrilling events. This simple yet captivating adventure offers endless fun and hours of joyful gameplay!

title: Cubie Jump
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)
description: Cubie Jump is an arcade game where you embark on a journey with your adorable Cubie & Cupet friends. Navigate changing landscapes, collect fruit to slow down, and employ double jumps strategically to progress further. With charming low-poly visuals and over 70 unique characters to unlock, the game offers immersive one-touch controls and endless excitement.

title: Sushi Factory
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)
description: Sushi Factory is a captivating puzzle game that puts your logic skills to the test. Place the sushi on top of the plate strategically to serve your guests and earn money. Solve challenging puzzles to unlock a variety of new sushi recipes and adorable sushi chef characters. Upgrade your restaurant's interior for a more delightful dining experience. Use helpful items to overcome challenges, and embark on missions to earn rewards. Explore the daily menu for additional surprises and prepare to be charmed by the irresistible cuteness of this sushi puzzle adventure while sharpening your mind along the way!

title: Jelly Snake
description: Jelly Snake is a unique snake game where only 1% of the super hand can go above level 100! From cute & simple levels to very difficult levels that developers have retried hundreds of times! Collect all the candies with Jelly Snakes that rotate left and right each time you touch them. Be careful not to hit wall, obstacles, and even monsters! You can reach higher levels only with your skills. Exchange the candies for cute snake decorations. Earn new jelly snakes with coins which you gain every time you clear a stage. Make the longest jelly snake in the world in challenge mode that will unlock at level 10. Win medals in challenge mode and get special exclusive Jelly Snakes. Try out various bizarre stages with brilliant ideas!

title: Bathroom Escape
description: Bathroom Escape is an escape game where you must solve all the puzzles to escape from the bathroom. Find any objects that can be useful, and also, use your logic and memory skills to solve the riddles.

title: Paper Plane Jam 3D
description: Paper Plane Jam 3D is a logic puzzle game where your goal is to guide all the paper planes to the correct place. Sort the planes, navigate through intricate mazes, and solve challenging puzzles as you take your paper plane to success. With a variety of engaging puzzles, you’ll test your problem-solving skills in different environments, each with increasing difficulty. Enjoy smooth controls that make the gameplay experience immersive. Let's play!

title: Art Tycoon
description: Idle Art Tycoon is a clicker game where you step into the shoes of a savvy entrepreneur aiming to build an art empire by harnessing the power of artificial intelligence. Train your AI to collect and wield paint blobs, manage servers, purchase upgrades, unlock achievements, research talents, track stats, and customize your gallery to showcase your AI's masterpieces. Let's dive into the key features of this captivating clicker game!

description: Rainbow Snake is a puzzle game where you must move the colored snakes through the board so they can stay on top of the same colored tiles. You can drag the snake's head or tail to move them around. Unleash your puzzle-solving skills. It seems easy at first, but the difficulty will increase as you go. There are interesting features such as movable blocks, blocking chickens, teleportation portals, etc. Have fun!

title: Noob: Zombie Prison Escape
description: Noob: Zombie Prison Escape is an action platforming game inspired by the style of Minecraft. Your mission is to help Noob escape from a zombie-infested prison by finding keys, coins, solving puzzles, avoiding traps, and using parkour skills to navigate platforms. Along the way, you'll need to shoot down monsters with a crossbow, complete tasks involving torches, and face various challenges in 10 different levels. Fans of the Noob series and Minecraft-style gameplay will find this game engaging as it features beloved characters and a variety of puzzles and adventures to solve.

Overcome obstacles and increasingly tougher enemies. You have to act directly on the environment with your trusty pencil and the inseparable eraser.

title: Lulu Run
platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android)

title: MIDNIGHT Remastered
description: This is the remastered edition of MIDNIGHT. Help the character to collect all the seven letters that are scattered in a dark and mysterious mansion.

title: Pogo Stick Parkour: Rage Game
description: Pogo Stick Parkour: Rage Game is a difficult 2D platformer game where you must use a pogo stick to overcome the path. Use your skills and jump around this surreal mountain full of different scenarios and impossible challenges. Try hard to avoid the frustration of falling. Will you be able to reach the top?

title: Gladiator: True Story
description: Gladiator: True Story is a gladiator arena survival game where you control Bruticus, the destroyer of worlds. This is the story of how you became the greatest gladiator of all time. Based on historical facts. Hack n' slash your way through waves of ultimate fighters and champions. Level up your armor and weapons to do even more damage in this bloody battle arena!

title: Cyber Cars Punk Racing
description: Cyber Cars Punk Racing is a 3D car driving game with futuristic cars and theme. There are super vehicles, neon city, and many game modes. 16 supercars, 60 racetracks, 2 players, 1 free ride area, Hot Pursuit area, and a battlefield are waiting for you. This game has a vehicle purchase and development system, and you can race against artificial intelligence or drive freely.

title: Real Cars in City
description: Real Cars in City is a 3D car simulation with superb graphics and various game modes. This game has realistic vehicle driving physics and quality graphics. There are 20 sports cars, 36 racetracks, 1 free ride area, a police chase area, and a crash derby area. There is a vehicle purchase and development system in the game. You can race against artificial intelligence or drive freely.

platform: Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), App Store(iOS, Android), Steam

Equip your weapon and start the action!

Use your fashion sense and your internal fashionista talent to create the best outfit for each princess girl. Choose a hairstyle, dress, gloves, shoes, wings, and other accessories for your princess girls. This game lets young fashionistas develop their taste and fashion designer skills.
